    <data key="d0">Epsagon: Automatically Tracing and Analyzing Billions of AWS Serverless Events</data>
    <data key="d1">https://www.youtube.com/watch?v=AzM_d7ZvzUE</data>
    <data key="d2">Epsagon processes billions of client Lambda invocations monthly by ingesting and parsing logs into structured metrics. It uses a serverless architecture to automatically scale and control costs.</data>
    <data key="d3">data_ingestion, compute_intensive</data>
    <data key="d4">True</data>
